-- Yahoo CEO says monthly traffic surpasses 800 million users
-- 
-- Wed Sep 11, 2013 7:30pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/09/11/net-us-yahoo-users-idUSBRE98A1AF20130911

 

 SAN FRANCISCO  (Reuters) - Yahoo Inc Chief Executive Marissa Mayer said the Internet company now has more than 800 million monthly active users, which she said represented 20 percent growth. 
 Speaking at the TechCrunch Disrupt conference in San Francisco on Wednesday, Mayer said the 800 million users did not include traffic from Tumblr, the online blog and social media hub that it acquired earlier this year. (Reporting by  Alexei Oreskovic )